variables.name: pattern
variables.comment:
* Entries are alg:prov separated by ,
         * Allow for prepended/appended whitespace between entries.
         *
         * Capture groups:
         *     1 - alg
         *     2 - :prov (optional)
         *     3 - prov (optional)
         *     4 - ,nextEntry (optional)
         *     5 - nextEntry (optional)
